The LED locations and functions match up with the [http://web.archive.org/web/20010406102510/http://bafo.com.tw/products-EBD3-1.htm BF-400 on the old Bafo website].
==Links of Interest== [http://support.lenovo.com/en_US/downloads/detail.page?DocID=PD004197 Noted as an accessory for the NetVista 6644, 6645, and 6646 models] :Presumed ~2000 release year
